The paper deals with the optimization problem of Max-SAT, which is a well-studied problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and theoretical computer science (cs.DS, cs.CC). The algorithm proposed in the paper involves estimating marginals over covers, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and probabilistic graphical models (cs.DM).
